title: Ladies Who Bitch with Becca Tobin, Keltie Knight and Jac Vanek of 'Ladygang'
description: Jackie and her new bffs from the Ladygang podcast (Becca Tobin, Keltie Knight & Jac Vanek) leave their manners at home and have a full throttle bitchfest. They discuss Jackies uber ride from hell, Bachelor nation inside scoop and mourning the tragic demise of Tiddleswift.
